<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>
<lb n="2"/>tēvarkku yāṇṭu patinē
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḻāvatu Uṭaiyār tirumaṇa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ñcēri Uṭaiyārkku pa
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉaiyūr nāṭṭuttūṟṟuk
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kuṭaiyāṉ nāṭuṭaiyā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṉ<unclear>vaitta</unclear> tirununtāviḷa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kku Oṉṟukku Ikkōyilil
<lb n="9"/>civappirāmaṇaṉ tillaināya 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kapaṭṭaṉum tirucciṟṟampalap
<lb n="11" break="no"/>paṭṭaṉum ceyyapātapaṭṭa
<lb n="12"/>ṉum tirumaṇañcēri paṭṭaṉum
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> paṭṭaṉum cantirāti
<lb n="14"/>ttavaṟ Upaiyañceluttak ko
<lb n="15"/>ṇṭakācu nāṟpattañcu Ittiru
<lb n="16"/>nuntāviḷakkeriya kōyilil
<lb n="17"/>Oṭukkiṉa tirukkuttiviḷakku Oṉṟi
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṉāl tarāniṟai nūṟṟu Eḻupattu mūṉṟu <g type="ddanda">.</g><g type="dashLong">.</g>
</p>

